I worked on a Secure and Scalable Digital Insurance Platform deployed on AWS. The project focused on automating infrastructure and application deployments using DevOps practices. We used AWS services like EC2, S3, IAM, RDS, and VPC for cloud infrastructure. CI/CD pipelines were implemented using Jenkins and Git to automate build and deployment processes. Terraform was used for Infrastructure as Code, and Docker with Kubernetes was used for containerization and orchestration. Monitoring and logging were handled using CloudWatch to ensure high availability and quick issue resolution in the production environment.
